cat > README.md << 'EOF'
# Eco-Brick Market Intelligence

Market analysis of 361 brick manufacturers across Telangana, India, to identify market gaps and optimal locations for an eco-brick venture.

Tools: Python (pandas, scikit-learn), Jupyter, and BI dashboards.

Note: data originates from a Google Maps scrape; this cleaned export is the earliest retained version and serves as the source of record.
